                    <li>Network Administration</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="extended-section" id="private-ai">
            <h2>Air-Gapped Private AI</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Deploy powerful Large Language Models directly on your own hardware. Zero data leaks. Zero cloud dependencies. Built for Treasure Valley law firms, clinics, and financial offices.</p>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Local LLM Deployment</h2>
                    <p>Custom Ollama and Open WebUI stacks tailored to your specific operational needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Absolute Data Privacy</h2>
                    <p>Your proprietary data never leaves your building. Complete mitigation of third-party API risks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Containerized & Secure</h2>
                    <p>Docker-based architecture ensuring isolated, highly maintainable, and secure AI nodes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="extended-section" id="custom-builds">
            <h2>Specialized Architecture</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Purpose-built hardware for demanding workloads. We engineer workstations optimized for extreme compute, deep rendering, and uncompromising security.</p>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>The AI Node</h2>
                    <p>Maximized VRAM and optimized tensor performance configured for running local language models and Docker natively.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Production Workstation</h2>
                    <p>Engineered for massive multi-threaded workloads, 3D geometric simulations, and complex audio processing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Zero-Trust Terminal</h2>
                    <p>Hardware selected for extreme opsec. Built to support security-focused hypervisors and hardware fingerprinting mitigation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="extended-section" id="onboarding">
            <h2>Initiate a Project</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Secure, confidential consultations for enterprise infrastructure and specialized architecture.</p>
            <form class="intake-form" action="mailto:admin@sheerai.net" method="POST" enctype="text/plain">
                <input type="text" name="Name" placeholder="Full Name / Point of Contact" required>
                <input type="text" name="Company" placeholder="Organization / Company">
                <input type="email" name="Email" placeholder="Secure Email Address" required>
                <select name="Service_Tier" required>
                    <option value="" disabled selected>Select Primary Objective...</option>
                    <option value="Private AI">Air-Gapped Private AI Deployment</option>
                    <option value="Custom Build">High-Performance Custom Architecture</option>
                    <option value="Zero Trust">Zero-Trust / Opsec Consulting</option>
                    <option value="Enterprise IT">Enterprise IT / Network Infrastructure</option>
                </select>
                <textarea name="Project_Scope" rows="5" placeholder="Briefly describe your current infrastructure and immediate requirements..." required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Request Secure Consultation</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-area">
            <a href="mailto:admin@sheerai.net" class="btn">Direct Email</a>
            <a href="https://portal.sheerai.net" class="btn btn-alt">Client Portal Login</a>
